                  <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t17170111-18-off91 t17170111-18-cd92"></join> last. The Prosecutor deposed, that going along Drury-lane, the Prisoner came up to him and saluted him with a How do you do, Countryman; Will you give me a Pint of Wine? And that tho' he did not promise her he would, yet he going into the <placeName id="t17170111-18-crimeloc93">Fountain-Tavern</placeName>
                  <interp inst="t17170111-18-crimeloc93" type="placeName" value="Fountain-Tavern"></interp>
